text: EA-2613 is an extremely toxic organophosphate nerve agent. It's an extremely potent acetylcholinesterase inhibitor that is resistant to atropine and oxime treatment. ==See also== *Nerve agent *EA-2012 *EA-2054 *EA-2098 ==References== Category:Organophosphate nerve agents Category:Acetylcholinesterase inhibitors Category:Quaternary ammonium compounds Category:Phenol ethers Category:Phenol esters Category:Phosphonate esters Category:Pinacolyl esters Category:Iodides
title: EA-2613
